README FILE FOR SWARM_ADAP

INSTALL:

o Place the tar in Swarm-NG's home directory, for example,
/home/username/swarm-ng/

o untar scatter-ng.tar.  This will unpack the following files.  All directories
are from the Swarm-NG's home directory.

	./ic/swarm_adap.py
	./run/adap_output/
	./src/user.h
	./src/swarm_adap/swarm_adap.h
	./src/swarm_adap/swarm_adap.cpp

o add the following lines to Makefile.user

	APPS+=swarm_adap
	swarm_adap_SOURCES=src/swarm_adap/swarm_adap.cpp

